        "subject": "LU-18225 build: remove virtio patch from el9.3-",
        "message": "LU-18225 build: remove virtio patch from el9.3-\n\nThe virtio_scsi-silence-page patch is causing build failures for el9.3\nkernels.  Since we will not be using these in the future, and the fix\nis only cosmetic, remove this patch from the older kernel series.\n\nBuild-Parameters: serverdistro=el9.3 arch=x86_64\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nFixes: 80a9e94df1 (\"LU-18225 kernel: silent page allocation failure in virtio_scsi\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0198c2274061369ec69376db9cf610d0962540e5\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
